summary: Wait professor, you let your Gengar siphon the life out of people?
question: Wait professor, you let your Gengar siphon the life out of people?
answer:
Well yes, but here’s the thing.

I don’t make Ray siphon enough energy to kill anyone. Just enough to make them very weak.

I only let him do it on people I approve. The real disgusting people in society. So what I’m doing is really chaotic good. At least, that’s what I think it should be.
